title: Alpine ranger: Mt. Buffalo National Park
brief_description: The Mount Buffalo National Park, north-eastern Victoria, throughout the year, showing visitors skiing, bush walking, climbing and fishing and the work of a park ranger in maintenance, supervision and fire control. No other credits available.
